{"tid":2055623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛突然改口叫人任何場合都要戴口罩 又係為左支那狗","createTime":"2020-06-08T06:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T04:48:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88d5b1fe800d3d150286177d39d18cab3454408d","tid":2055623,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"中國口罩產能過剩 投機成立口罩廠恐血本無歸<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情爆發後，口罩成為各國搶購的目標。有台灣媒體報道，內地下月將出現口罩產能過剩，部分企業擬改為出口。不過，當地3月後才成立投產的口罩廠恐怕血本無歸。 <br />\n<br />\n據中國國家發改委統計，中國口罩日產量達1.16億個。不過，據台灣媒體報道指出，業界有人估計，實際產量可能更高，甚至每日產能高達2億個。雖然3月底至4月，當地將會全需復課、復工，故需求高峰期將會延續至4月。<br />\n<br />\n然而，高峰期過後，業界估計口罩需求量會回落到每天1億個以下，單次使用醫用口罩的售價將會在5月內由人民幣4元趺至2元。據了解，目前中國國內有60%的新增口罩企業是在3月後才成立投產，有不少「投機玩家」加入市場。該報道，有業界人士估計有多達百萬人加入口罩生產行列。<br />\n<br />\n全球疫情仍未受控，歐美等地仍有一定的口罩需求，故不少中國口罩商亦會轉投出口。不過，自3月開始，口罩生產相關的人工、材料、設備成本升超過10倍，而口罩才升逾3倍多。業界稱，眾多人加入口罩生產線的情況下，口罩的核心原材料熔噴不織布，價格更是從原來的每噸人民幣2萬元，被炒到最高55萬元。 3月後才進入的新產商，很可能會血本無歸。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2594931/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%A2%E8%83%BD%E9%81%8E%E5%89%A9%E3%80%80%E6%8A%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%BB%A0%E6%81%90%E8%A1%80%E6%9C%AC%E7%84%A1%E6%AD%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2594931%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%2594%25A2%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2589%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25AD%25B8&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=4223e401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2594931/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%A2%E8%83%BD%E9%81%8E%E5%89%A9%E3%80%80%E6%8A%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%BB%A0%E6%81%90%E8%A1%80%E6%9C%AC%E7%84%A1%E6%AD%B8</a>"},{"pid":"80b4922e1ec8e11b0e5cea0f9447b1a89c0ab982","tid":2055623,"uid":81052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3347f416c690a8dca5d3e804e37250df76ab2e30","tid":2055623,"uid":186882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"我一早已經話支那一定大攪口罩經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴既口罩假既又防唔到肺炎病毒戴黎托"},{"pid":"af08ca3cfa7b77fa45ded5ceb836753d3951476d","tid":2055623,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"香港政府會接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f541094d2394c59d27afd23c23f0bec454d310f7","tid":2055623,"uid":119250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"啲罩唔合標準 仲有人敢要咩"},{"pid":"26ab7bbc292805a6e98a41c04d2df8c6ddc92e53","tid":2055623,"uid":185656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f541094d2394c59d27afd23c23f0bec454d310f7","tid":2055623,"uid":119250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"啲罩唔合標準 仲有人敢要咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"先唔講合唔合格<br />\n佢哋本身標準都低過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429a5b7dcbd468d3f50bd4b8daa2fbad6b0f94d3","tid":2055623,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"同我推上熱門啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「反國安法」23個工會x中學生罷課平台發起三罷公投！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2055628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2055628</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99e00091fecd6828cb486d37f67d